{"about_the_game":"What if the physical objects of everyday life, the possessions we hold close, were actual windows to the past? Peer into distant memories and unseen futures in Hindsight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122700/extras/chrysalis.gif?t=1729099970\" /><br><br>From the creator of Prune, Hindsight is a narrative exploration game spanning the entirety of a woman's life, from birth to present day, as she tries to make sense of it all. Revisit her childhood home, sort through personal belongings, and step through windows to memories frozen in time. <br><br>Hindsight asks you to slow down and pay attention to the little things left behind. Piece these things together and shift your viewpoint until you find just the right perspective to pull you deeper into the past.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122700/extras/clothes_line.gif?t=1729099970\" /><br><br>Long forgotten memories and dreams cascade into one another. Linger as long as you wish, but sooner or later you must come back to the present. <br><br>What will you take with you? And what will you leave behind?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Still Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1122700/3d2a16efc45a3f160eb2422610fe91563d151cae.jpg"},{"name":"Within The Lines","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1122700/d444a0d0ae1794054bb867fdae76a7427376fa58.jpg"},{"name":"Falling Into Place","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1122700/e31819ecaf64e9e3891e658f8def64e132108d93.jpg"},{"name":"Pulled Under","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1122700/c26cc4d85b8ef1bd7f1581e5f86b574a2c2aedc5.jpg"},{"name":"Mise En Place","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1122700/